ith CYP450 3A4 inhibitors, particularly potent and moderate inhibitors (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/27388/', '', 'Dextromethorphan, Clofedanol, Benzonatate, Pentoxyverine, Codeine', 'Dirithromycin, Lincomycin, Azithromycin, Clindamycin', 1767369485);
